          "title": "A broadly generalizable stabilization strategy for sarbecovirus fusion machinery vaccines",
          "authorString": "Lee J, Stewart C, Schaefer A, Leaf EM, Park Y, Asarnow D, Powers JM, Treichel C, Corti D, Baric R, King NP, Veesler D.",
